== Spanish == 
=== Transitive Verb === 
'''acabar'''
# to [[finish]]; to [[end]]
'''acabar de'''
# to have just
#: ''Acabo de leer el libro.'' - "I just read that book."
'''acabar con'''
# to [[finish]]; to put an end to
#: ''Acaba con la doble injusticia.'' - "Put an end to the double injustice."

